    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/2120c9b22c246499ac27a674ad8df4af.avif?t=1667328331\" width=560 height=184 /></span><br><br>旅居者之信，是一个关于建立人际关系以及和他人建立联系的叙事性纸牌游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/1854b1bb50c71e82f00f49878aced1d0.poster.avif?t=1667328331\" width=560 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/1854b1bb50c71e82f00f49878aced1d0.webm?t=1667328331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/1854b1bb50c71e82f00f49878aced1d0.mp4?t=1667328331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你桌面上的牌是您的角色，它反映了您的经历并且塑造了您的人际关系。您要决定您在这个世界里的角色，并利用好自己手里的牌。<br><br>母亲去世后，您接手了这个小店，前往世界各地为小店采购物品。旅途艰辛，气候变化让旅途更加艰难。在此过程中您会邂逅乐观的故事、富有同情心的人和充满意外的惊喜。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要内容</h2><br>通过纸牌游戏对话建立新的友谊，对抗和联系。利用您手里的牌组去匹配同伴的态度和观点，或者忽略他们的感受以表达自己的观点让故事继续。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/9814956ca90ad8044e8f652ebddf13c5.poster.avif?t=1667328331\" width=560 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/9814956ca90ad8044e8f652ebddf13c5.webm?t=1667328331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/9814956ca90ad8044e8f652ebddf13c5.mp4?t=1667328331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>冒险去寻找稀有、有用的物品来帮助您的家乡。一路上您将作出许多艰难的选择，这些结果将塑造您角色手里的牌组以及随后和游戏中不同人物进行的每次对话，并最终影响不同的结局。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/41368ef6130bc6c9edf04eddf611271a.poster.avif?t=1667328331\" width=560 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/41368ef6130bc6c9edf04eddf611271a.webm?t=1667328331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/41368ef6130bc6c9edf04eddf611271a.mp4?t=1667328331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您将探索世界，同时也探索返回家园的意义。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/91a76713158374beef9d6ae6dc697ada.poster.avif?t=1667328331\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/91a76713158374beef9d6ae6dc697ada.webm?t=1667328331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/91a76713158374beef9d6ae6dc697ada.mp4?t=1667328331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>与难忘的人物会面并一起成长，您会坚持您的童年友谊吗？您在旅途中的冒险会带领您走上不同的道路吗？您将成为谁，您将留下什么？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/4c00c6342cf85e41624a33303413dcc8.poster.avif?t=1667328331\" width=560 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/4c00c6342cf85e41624a33303413dcc8.webm?t=1667328331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058690/extras/4c00c6342cf85e41624a33303413dcc8.mp4?t=1667328331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>我们很抱歉此游戏暂不支持简体中文。我看好你的英文哟！",
